          "The parallels between drone warfare and Agentic USD are not merely conceptual. They represent a convergence of strategic doctrine, operational methodology, and technological capability that suggests a unified approach to power projection. Just as drone technology disrupted military doctrine in the 2000s and 2010s by enabling remote, persistent, and scalable strikes without visible military infrastructure, Agentic USD is disrupting monetary doctrine in the 2020s by enabling remote, persistent, and scalable capital flows without visible financial infrastructure. Both operate at machine speed. Both bypass traditional defenses. Both fundamentally erode the sovereignty of target nations. And both have already demonstrated their effectiveness in real-world operations.",
