          "This principle is not limited to the animal kingdom. It applies with equal force to warfare and finance. In both domains, the faster system defeats the slower system. The drone with AI-in-command defeats the human-controlled air defense system. The Agentic USD with machine-speed capital allocation defeats the human-controlled central bank. Speed is the decisive factor. Not strength. Not resources. Not traditional weapons. Speed determines dominance, and in the modern era, speed belongs to machines."
