          "The UK's Specific Imperatives: The United Kingdom faces specific vulnerabilities. It is dependent on US military protection through NATO. It is dependent on US financial infrastructure through the dollar-based global financial system. It is vulnerable to both drone strikes and Agentic USD infiltration. Immediate actions (0-12 months) include establishing on-chain monitoring capabilities, beginning CBDC development acceleration, and developing Double-Backed stablecoin framework. Medium-term actions (1-3 years) include deploying CBDC infrastructure, building alternative payment networks, and developing indigenous drone capabilities. Long-term actions (3-10 years) include achieving monetary independence from Agentic USD, achieving military independence from US drone technology, and establishing the UK as an independent power center."
